{"tid":1232121,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港人覺醒] 生在籠裡的鳥 認為飛翔是一種病","createTime":"2019-06-16T14:37:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T16:34:17.000Z","uid":36359,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"01a6ee44d2cfcd6e9278e5dbcbad8c8378242adc","tid":1232121,"uid":36359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:37:07.000Z","msg":"好多人係政治冷感 口腔期最緊要食玩訓 <br />\n佢地係太平盛世成長 由細到大個社會都係欣欣向榮 冇咁多不公不義 根本唔知咩叫抗爭<br />\n所以一見到人行出黎就話人搞事<br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">生在籠裡的鳥，認為飛翔是一種病</span></div></strong><br />\n<br />\n但一個正常智力又肯去了解既人 係冇乜可能唔支持自由民主<br />\n<br />\n希望香港人覺醒 唔好怕抗爭 要習慣不平則鳴 擇善固執 據理力爭<br />\n唔好怕 唔好覺得多你一個唔多 唔好覺得點都改變唔到<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">今日遊行果200萬人出哂黎投票既話 <br />\n根本可以踢哂保皇黨出議會 一個不留!</span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"830ada3f321baedd6c8fbf778e090fe64ba6ad5a","tid":1232121,"uid":36359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:43:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a147322b36671ae320bee99b1b9c9a684210788e","tid":1232121,"uid":36359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:51:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eddae95a0adba1ce541e36232ba2951386c5bde7","tid":1232121,"uid":36359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:56:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75cf694e4f72356a12463a8ea9c30c31bf98c368","tid":1232121,"uid":36359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"436494b48b0314e355d40b83a6282b211bdb997f","tid":1232121,"uid":36359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:23:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" clas